### COVID19 Deaths in DC
```{r echo = FALSE}
gen_covid %>%

  ggplot() +
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = `Number of Deaths`, y = `Cleared From Isolation`)) +
  geom_smooth(aes(`Number of Deaths`,`Cleared From Isolation`), method="lm") +
  labs (
    title = "Relation of Number of Deaths to COVID19 Patients Cleared from Isolation",
    x = "Number of Deaths",
    y = "Cleared From Isolation"
  )+
   theme_minimal()
```

### COVID19 Deaths Compared to Those Released from Isolation





```{r echo = FALSE}
new_df %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_line(mapping = aes(x = dates, y = frequency, color = type)) +
  labs (
    title = "Number of Deaths and COVID19 Patients Cleared from Isolation Over Time",
    x = "Date",
    y = "Frequency"
  ) +
   theme_minimal()

```


